Users unaware of setting changes
Unskilled users cannot decide whether they should swipe or tap, and they may inadvertently change the setting by tapping unintentionally to close it after a long press.

Users change settings unintentionally, and without realizing it, they say that it is difficult to use the system. I think it would be a good idea to add a function to the system that asks, "You made this change yesterday, was this intentional?


